Ant : Nobody is trying to make you ashamed of being white, you farking morons!!! You'd understand that if you weren't so farking stupid!
Yeah I don't get that, at all. I'm white, and it's not like I feel some weird cultural identity with the jackasses running the government at the moment. Nor would I expect to. Nor would I understand why the fark anyone would figure it mattered. As far as I can tell what it comes down to is, "Those brown people have something I don't - even if it's repression and imposed-bullshiat fueled forced community. If they got it I want it to!1BBQ" That attitude confuses me sideways and back again. The whole "everybody with vaguely similar skin color is a monolithic group with X attitudes" thing needs to screw off and die already.
/and I'm 48, so these older farks have no excuse either
//hate that "Well they just grew up in a different time" crap
///so did I. I learned stuff. I grew the hell up. If I had to, so do they
